1、一定要先安装需要的一些底层的编译依赖
conda install -c conda-forge hdf5 libxml2 zlib curl openssl





1、安装BiocManager
if (!requireNamespace("BiocManager", quietly = TRUE))
    install.packages("BiocManager")

2、安装glmGamPoi需要的依赖
BiocManager::install(c("Rhdf5lib", "rhdf5filters", "rhdf5", "XVector", 
                       "SparseArray", "DelayedArray", "beachmat", 
                       "DelayedMatrixStats", "HDF5Array", 
                       "SummarizedExperiment", "SingleCellExperiment"))
3、安装glmGamPoi
BiocManager::install("glmGamPoi")





